data.description: True brick built home on 1+ acre lot w/an inground saltwater pool, attached 2car garage, detached garage/workshop & 14' 6" tall RV shelter w/electrical hookup. Over 2,900sqft, this home has 3BR's, 2.5 baths & a huge bonus rm w/a closet. Oversized family rm. Large eat-in kitchen w/Corian counters, gas range & custom pantry. Screened porch leads to the 30x30 covered deck which is perfect for entertaining. 2 Car detached garage/workshop w/electricity & water, perfect place for your hobbies, storage, or even a home business. Solid built home w/Ext walls are 8" concrete block reinforced w/concrete/steel, int of block is furred w/metal studs & finished w/sheetrock. 1"of insulation between sheetrock & 8"block, ext of block has 2"rigid insulation (total of 16" from sheetrock to brick). The crawlspace is also encapsulated, ensuring that your home is warm and dry year-round. Country living w/no HOA or city taxes & only 30 mins to Ft.Liberty. The riding lawn mower is negotiable!
